{"tid":680234,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩屌，呢隻高級五毛都隱藏得幾深，差啲以為佢係獨派！","createTime":"2018-05-27T05:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T04:11:04.000Z","uid":90,"like":63,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0e60e6d33cdfec48de2943885e8e8aacde017b","tid":680234,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"1. 玩支那game(間接/直接支援支那）<br />\n[url][A/I] PUBG Mobile 連登食雞竇 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/642704/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/642704/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n*事關早前<span style=\"color: red;\">支那騰訊</span>遊戲重金買下了遊戲的手機版本開發、代理權後，今日就正式於國際市場推出了《PUBG》的手機版 － 《PUBG Mobile》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.睇TVB（間接支持tvb洗港人腦）<br />\n[url]無間道 TVB 討論區 (1) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/534168/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/534168/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n3. 假膠又唔好笑（疑似洗走重要新聞）<br />\n[url]全港中學最快下周一停課 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/520447/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/520447/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n*再引用權威評論<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/130112_8816bfd870bb58cd526ae0cf0c2b4401.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F130112_8816bfd870bb58cd526ae0cf0c2b4401.png&h=6627503c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 不停鳩叫以死相博，疑似想推義士/本土派支持者去死<br />\n[url]香 港 獨 立 ，以 死 相 搏 ! <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/678860/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/678860/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n5.不停同一篇文不停重複開post，疑似洗走重要新聞（一堆民族黨香港獨立論說，但開過不下10次）<br />\n[url]香 港 獨 立 ！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/449897/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/449897/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n6. 十足BOT咁，同蛋牛麵個啲五毛一樣<br />\nPost完啲嘢，剩係識用icon同圖去覆人<br />\n從來未見過佢好似人類咁講嘢<br />\n<br />\n7.波台<br />\n[url]【科蘭踢亞冠】 傑志 對 全北汽車 20/2  (2) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/566989/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/566989/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n呢啲撚屌，剩係識上網鳩叫<br />\n精神勝利法，呢啲就真係抺黑港獨<br />\n毁滅本土派形象嘅垃圾賤種狗<br />\n屌你老母大大聲「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以死相博</span></span><br />\n想問博撚咗去邊撚到<br />\n咪撚同我講乜撚嘢打擊本土派，冇可能衝<br />\n係條撚屌自己講先，唔撚係講完自己唔撚做掛？咁你講乜鳩？獨乜鳩<br />\n日日上網貼圖就夠喇<br />\n呢啲垃圾剩係引人去做，自己鳩叫<br />\n唔屌撚柒呢啲人渣，你十世都唔使有進展<br />\n呢啲港獨派/本土派嘅寄生蟲<br />\n剩係圍爐打J,叫人做嘢<br />\n得個網絡統戰<br />\n你話重要，is ok<br />\n拉啲中立派，係的確有用<br />\n但呢啲垃圾真係趕客多過拉人入獨派<br />\n做極啲嘢都係畀人笑<br />\n唔好話五毛打手喇，是但一個中立少少理性少少嘅人都想笑柒呢啲網絡統戰員喇<br />\n屌你老母，剩係識話五毛<br />\n完全唔撚識反省自己有幾咁撚柒<br />\n好彩你地只係識上連登9up<br />\n如果畀你參選，做到下個本民前，青政，民族黨<br />\n港獨真係等收皮都得，成班仲撚垃圾過共狗販民<br />\n屌你老母以後用下你地個死人腦諗完先講嘢喇"},{"pid":"03c8820acae63f6bcabf9e350f8a18bebe9e5b96","tid":680234,"uid":33642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"全力炮轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cc33f12044120419ad4c676e7d74b922b5973e","tid":680234,"uid":58140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"個背景幾靚 點換"},{"pid":"bc4cf8130def274f887e8075d715ccb93833e570","tid":680234,"uid":90,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cc33f12044120419ad4c676e7d74b922b5973e","tid":680234,"uid":58140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"個背景幾靚 點換"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"設定有"},{"pid":"09f23b4b768a391a3b3725ce484bd35a1eb12abd","tid":680234,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"巨乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 